metadata.name: Mega OG Akutar Mint Pass
metadata.description: An Akutar Mint Pass grants you a FREE Akutar via an Airdrop if held during the wallet snapshot on April 22, 2022 at 2 pm EST They also grant you a .5 ETH Discount off the final Public Sale price. Example: 3 Mints with 3 Passes in your wallet at snapshot= 1.5 ETH Total Discount. After the Wallet Snapshot on April 22, 2022 at 2 pm EST these passes will no longer be able to redeem an Akutar. Akutars are a collection of 15,000 unique, 3D Aku avatars with a few special traits from six different collaborators. There are 3 tiers of Akutar Airdrop Passes: - Random Akutar - Akutar with an OG Trait - Akutar with a Mega OG Trait
